♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:04.321 --> 00:42:08.691
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:42:08.956 --> 00:42:13.086
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:13.271 --> 00:42:18.846
